  dialogueLines:
  - It's time to start catching fish!
  - Click the fish to get a bite and your catch box will appear!
  - The longer you hold the left click down the higher the green catch box will go!
  - Keep the fish inside the green catch box to fill up your catch meter!
  - When the catch meter is full, you'll have caught the fish!
  - Why don't you give it a go...
